.Dd $Mdocdate: June 8 2025 $
.Dt LLDP 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm lldp
.Nd control the lldpd agent
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm lldp
.Op Fl v
.Op Fl i Ar interface
.Op Fl s Ar socket
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
program communicates with the
.Xr lldpd 8
Link Layer Discovery Protocol (LLDP)
agent to fetch and display LLDP entries received by the agent.
.Pp
The options are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl i Ar interface
Limit the LLDP entries to those received on the specified
.Ar interface .
.It Fl s Ar socket
Use
.Ar socket
to communicate with
.Xr lldpd 8 .
.It Fl v
Increase the verbosity of output.
.El
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width "/var/run/lldp.sock" -compact
.It Pa /var/run/lldp.sock
default
.Xr lldpd 8
control socket
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr lldpd 8
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
program first appeared in
.Ox 7.8 .
